Interface Log<T extends Template>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LgChain, LgConsole, LgFile, LgLimited, LgTcp, LgUdp

    public interface Log<T extends Template>
    Log interface. Implementations of the Log interface must use Templates to ensure that logs conform to the same standard. Logs of one standard are easier to parse using Grok or Regex and so on.
    See Also:
    Template, Grok
